MoView version 0.1

MoView allows you to obtain most important movie data from imdb.com and choose what's worth seeing tonight.

Final results list is rendered as index.html page placed in the MoView execution directory.

Usage:

python moview.py file_name - extracts imdb data for a single movie

python moview.py directory_name - extracts imdb data for a single directory

python moview.py -s file_name - extracts imdb data for a single movie

python moview.py -f directory_name - extracts imdb data for a single directory

python moview.py -r directory_name - extracts imdb data scaning recursivly all directories for direcotry_name

Please note: in the current version (0.1) not recognized movies are not added to the results list rendered in index.html file.

Greetings:
MoView uses css template obtained from http://www.freecsstemplates.org 
MoVIew uses hash calculating method obatined from opensubtitles.org
imdb.com community for creating imdb python module

Enjoy!
